>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocomhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgpaocomhk%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c673e279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocomhk/</a><br />\n(HkG pao2.0,收過皮一次,依家有2萬followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F393490971355994%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b3be8a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/393490971355994/?ref=share</a><br />\n(萬惡之源savehk群組,17萬members<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=af5823f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ</a><br />\n(臭閪藍天使陳怡,近18萬subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/arsing1225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Farsing1225&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=3c3f096e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/arsing1225</a><br />\n(臭閪異號曾鎧琪,近9萬subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fleetszking&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=816af221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/leetszking</a><br />\n(最近view數爆升嘅閪門梓,過10萬subscribe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多,下面整合再pin....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong>3)改變上網習慣,有系統打擊五毛</strong></strong></span></span><br />\n有睇開rthk,now,cable呢類大新聞page就知<br />\n對家五毛基本上一直好有策略玩鍵戰<br />\n佢地識集中互like同reply去推自己人留言<br />\n但手足們好多時見到藍絲/五毛就忍唔住理論<br />\n結果變咗幫手拉自己人留言落底<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>所以平時上網請堅守以下原則</strong></span><br />\n1)睇新聞/live時多留言,互相附和<br />\n2)互like留言,俾多d唔同表情沖散五毛俾嘅嬲<br />\n3)勿覆五毛,嬲都唔好比(除非層主係自己人)<br />\n4)見到明顯假acc記得舉報<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>4)警暴注目度嚴重不足</strong></span></span><br />\n狗暴從來冇停,以下係近個幾月冰山一角嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾著半年前呢度每一單都係核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但慢慢由嬲完繼續返工進化到連嬲都慳返<br />\n班狗已經係fb狂出po+開記招扮勤力<br />\n加上政府拍哂片777飛埋去外國瘋狂洗白<br />\n再咁落去班狗好快會攞返班中立港豬嘅信任(唔好以為個個都咁堅定)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WpHDd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WpHDd9.png&h=52ff4b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmJ9iea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmJ9iea.png&h=8d0e06c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFdJnFR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFdJnFR.png&h=99385169&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kz4sPkS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKz4sPkS.png&h=6a6d3ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DH5Dbzd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDH5Dbzd.png&h=999d9ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0M94Rze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0M94Rze.png&h=28008c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QADbzg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2